oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Original wills, Baker, John L., 1853 November 11
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An original will of John L. Baker, dated November 11th, 1853. Illustrates the first page of the document. The notation on the verso: “Recorded in Will & Invy. Book 19, Page 426.” Forms part of Record Group 16, Original Wills, 1780-1925.
